<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 06:09:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的联盟看起来很安全，因为就连他的对手也拒绝了哈马斯的停火提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-looks-safe-as-even-his-opponents-reject-hamas-cease-fire-offer/0000018f-54e7-d209-a79f-54ef7bc10000</link><description>民族团结部长和以色列谈判团队反对加沙恐怖组织的提议，该提议与以色列接受的提议在三个关键方面有所不同，其中包括哈马斯拒绝保证在协议第一阶段释放人质。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 03:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-looks-safe-as-even-his-opponents-reject-hamas-cease-fire-offer/0000018f-54e7-d209-a79f-54ef7bc10000</guid></item><item><title>官员称，美国暂停向以色列运送炸弹，以表达对拉法入侵的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article-live/u-s-israel-agrees-to-open-kerem-shalom-crossing-for-aid-into-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018f-5600-d0ec-a9cf-de1fb30d0000</link><description>美国表示，以色列同意周三开放凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点，以向加沙提供援助 ■ 疑似以色列人质于 10 月 7 日被杀，尸体关押在加沙 ■ 以色列承诺限制拉法行动，将与埃及过境点的控制权授予美国私人公司 ■ 哈马斯驻加沙代表团开罗举行人质谈判 ■ 国防部长加兰特：在消灭哈马斯或释放第一名人质之前，拉法行动不会停止</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 02:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article-live/u-s-israel-agrees-to-open-kerem-shalom-crossing-for-aid-into-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018f-5600-d0ec-a9cf-de1fb30d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的拉法袭击和停火谈判并不像看上去的那样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/nothing-about-israels-rafah-attack-and-the-cease-fire-talks-is-quite-what-it-seems/0000018f-5484-d6a5-a5ff-d6a402c80000</link><description>停火迫在眉睫吗？以色列如何才能在谈判达成协议的同时占领拉法口岸？哈马斯和埃及的游戏计划是什么？内塔尼亚胡能否在不跨越拜登红线的情况下安抚本格维尔？以下是如何了解加沙正在发生的事情以及战争是否会很快结束</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 21:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/nothing-about-israels-rafah-attack-and-the-cease-fire-talks-is-quite-what-it-seems/0000018f-5484-d6a5-a5ff-d6a402c80000</guid></item><item><title>白宫称以色列和哈马斯之间在停火协议上的分歧可以弥合</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/white-house-says-gaps-between-israel-and-hamas-on-cease-fire-deal-can-be-bridged/0000018f-5491-d209-a79f-54b93a7b0000</link><description>白宫发言人否认美国在哈马斯同意的拟议协议上背着以色列 ■ 拜登政府警告内塔尼亚胡不要扩大拉法的入侵，但也表示对费城路线沿线的行动没有问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 20:53:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/white-house-says-gaps-between-israel-and-hamas-on-cease-fire-deal-can-be-bridged/0000018f-5491-d209-a79f-54b93a7b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯代表团抵达开罗，信号混乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-back-in-cairo-amid-mixed-signals/0000018f-5483-d4c7-a3af-fcfb4e360000</link><description>以色列一直在传播相互矛盾的信息。一方面，战时内阁同意继续谈判，另一方面，政治消息人士称谈判是“欺骗”，旨在削弱拉法行动</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 20:00:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-back-in-cairo-amid-mixed-signals/0000018f-5483-d4c7-a3af-fcfb4e360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人嘲笑亲巴勒斯坦校园抗议活动是在玩火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-07/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-who-ridicule-pro-palestinian-campus-protests-are-playing-with-fire/0000018f-5399-d4c7-a3af-fffb83820000</link><description>以色列人若不理会这些抗议活动，后果自负。他们的未来在很多方面取决于这些在世界最负盛名的大学草坪上露营的学生所形成的观点，以及他们将对其国家未来政策产生的影响</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 19:56:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-07/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-who-ridicule-pro-palestinian-campus-protests-are-playing-with-fire/0000018f-5399-d4c7-a3af-fffb83820000</guid></item><item><title>人质家庭论坛：疑似人质利奥尔·鲁达夫 (Lior Rudaeff) 于 10 月 7 日被杀，他的尸体被扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/presumed-hostage-lior-rudaeff-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-is-held-in-gaza/0000018f-5486-d209-a79f-54afd6b50000</link><description>鲁达夫是紧急安全小组的成员，10 月 7 日，他与数十名渗入尼尔伊扎克基布兹的恐怖分子进行了战斗。鲁达夫身后留下了妻子、四个孩子和三个孙子</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 19:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/presumed-hostage-lior-rudaeff-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-is-held-in-gaza/0000018f-5486-d209-a79f-54afd6b50000</guid></item><item><title>人质、停火谈判将决定拉法行动的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/hostage-cease-fire-talks-will-determine-the-future-of-rafah-operation/0000018f-544c-d209-a79f-546d94040000</link><description>以色列军队已经控制了拉​​法过境点和费城走廊东部，向哈马斯施压，要求达成人质交易。但这可能会导致对拉法的征服——这有可能导致谈判破裂并危及人质的生命</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 19:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/hostage-cease-fire-talks-will-determine-the-future-of-rafah-operation/0000018f-544c-d209-a79f-546d94040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何仍能赢得对哈马斯和伊朗的最终胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-israel-can-still-win-the-ultimate-victory-over-hamas-and-iran/0000018f-4ee0-d6c3-afdf-4ff322520000</link><description>以色列的“单干”战略猛然醒悟：它需要美国和阿拉伯盟友更多的支持来对抗伊朗及其恶毒伙伴，包括哈马斯和真主党。拜登的战后计划提供了这条生命线，但总统还应该添加一个元素</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 18:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-israel-can-still-win-the-ultimate-victory-over-hamas-and-iran/0000018f-4ee0-d6c3-afdf-4ff322520000</guid></item><item><title>美国缓慢向以色列出售武器引发政策转变问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-slow-rolling-weapons-sale-to-israel-sparking-questions-of-policy-shift/0000018f-541a-d6a5-a5ff-d63a538f0000</link><description>尽管拜登政府实际上已暂停向以色列出售武器，但官员们否认了这标志着政策新转变的说法，尽管美以因迫在眉睫的拉法行动而关系紧张</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-slow-rolling-weapons-sale-to-israel-sparking-questions-of-policy-shift/0000018f-541a-d6a5-a5ff-d63a538f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列发起拉法行动的威胁奏效了——但主要是针对埃及和美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-threat-of-a-rafah-operation-worked-but-mainly-against-egypt-and-the-u-s/0000018f-53ca-d348-a7bf-f7eb45ce0000</link><description>哈马斯的声明开启了达成停火协议的可能性。如果实现的话，也可能影响北部战线，并为与黎巴嫩外交解决打开渠道</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-threat-of-a-rafah-operation-worked-but-mainly-against-egypt-and-the-u-s/0000018f-53ca-d348-a7bf-f7eb45ce0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登通过谴责 10 月 7 日的否认主义和美国反犹太主义的高涨来纪念大屠杀日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-holocaust-day-by-condemning-oct-7-denialism-rising-antisemitism-in-america/0000018f-53e7-d4c7-a3af-ffff9ce70000</link><description>拜登在美国国会大厦举行的官方大屠杀纪念仪式上发表主旨演讲时表示，“我们现在不是75年后，而是仅仅七个半月后——人们已经忘记了哈马斯发动了这场恐怖袭击”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:20:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-holocaust-day-by-condemning-oct-7-denialism-rising-antisemitism-in-america/0000018f-53e7-d4c7-a3af-ffff9ce70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列承诺限制拉法行动，将与埃及过境的控制权授予美国私营公司</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-commits-to-limit-rafah-operation-grant-control-of-crossing-to-private-u-s-firm/0000018f-53ee-d6a5-a5ff-d3eeaf700000</link><description>地面入侵拉法之前，以色列在会谈中明确表示，此次行动的目的是在人质谈判中向哈马斯施加压力，并损害该过境点作为哈马斯权力象征的声誉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-commits-to-limit-rafah-operation-grant-control-of-crossing-to-private-u-s-firm/0000018f-53ee-d6a5-a5ff-d3eeaf700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 214 天：以色列代表团抵达埃及进行停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-214-israeli-delegation-lands-in-egypt-for-cease-fire-talks/0000018f-53e0-d6a5-a5ff-d3e075da0001</link><description>以色列国防军控制了拉法过境点的巴勒斯坦一侧 ■ 官员称，以色列代表团抵达埃及继续停火谈判 ■ 以色列总理内塔尼亚胡表示，哈马斯同意的提议与以色列的要求相去甚远，主要区别在于是否会释放活人质或死人质国土报 ■ 辛贝特局长在欧洲歌唱大赛前访问瑞典检查安全程序 ■ 战争结束 214 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 16:45:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-214-israeli-delegation-lands-in-egypt-for-cease-fire-talks/0000018f-53e0-d6a5-a5ff-d3e075da0001</guid></item><item><title>Telegrass 以色列杂草市场创始人因经营犯罪组织被判 8 年徒刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/telegrass-weed-marketplace-founder-sentenced-to-8-years-for-running-criminal-organization/0000018f-532f-dc9e-a7df-573febbf0000</link><description>经过长达五年的法律斗争，阿莫斯·多夫·西尔弗（Amos Dov Silver）和 Telegrass 的其他员工（该公司成为大麻和其他非法物质的交易渠道）被判犯有一系列毒品交易罪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:54:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/telegrass-weed-marketplace-founder-sentenced-to-8-years-for-running-criminal-organization/0000018f-532f-dc9e-a7df-573febbf0000</guid></item><item><title>IDI民意调查发现，大多数以色列人优先考虑哈马斯人质交易而不是拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/majority-of-israelis-prioritize-hamas-hostage-deal-over-rafah-operation-idi-poll-finds/0000018f-5364-dcda-abcf-7b679a700000</link><description>以色列民主研究所的一项民意调查显示，56% 的以色列犹太人和 88% 的阿拉伯人认为，以色列应该优先考虑人质协议而不是拉法攻势——他们中的大多数人都认同政治左翼或中间派观点，而右翼则更喜欢由以色列人发起的军事攻击。薄边距</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/majority-of-israelis-prioritize-hamas-hostage-deal-over-rafah-operation-idi-poll-finds/0000018f-5364-dcda-abcf-7b679a700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队控制了拉法边境口岸的巴勒斯坦一侧，部队在该市东部活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-takes-control-of-palestinian-side-of-rafah-border-crossing/0000018f-51eb-d6c3-afdf-5dfbc7980000</link><description>随着人质谈判取得重大进展，以色列国防军已经控制了通往埃及的拉法过境点的巴勒斯坦一侧以及凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点，该过境点现已关闭，禁止人道主义援助进入。以色列消息人士向美国有线电视新闻网表示：“这次入侵是一次有限的行动，旨在迫使哈马斯同意达成协议”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:44:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-takes-control-of-palestinian-side-of-rafah-border-crossing/0000018f-51eb-d6c3-afdf-5dfbc7980000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列，崇拜圣战之神的犹太极端分子正在变得越来越强大</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-israel-jewish-extremists-worshipping-a-god-of-holy-war-are-getting-stronger/0000018f-496c-d17f-adcf-f9ef43630000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列右翼犹太激进分子公然反民主、道德沦丧的政治神学、为巴勒斯坦人的死亡、饥饿和饥饿辩护的世界观正变得更加占主导地位。以色列和世界各地的犹太人必须面对这种对我们传统的亵渎</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 07:31:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-israel-jewish-extremists-worshipping-a-god-of-holy-war-are-getting-stronger/0000018f-496c-d17f-adcf-f9ef43630000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在真主党无人机袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-hezbollah-drone-strike/0000018f-5169-d6c3-afdf-5d7b6efc0000</link><description>两名预备役军人在黎巴嫩边境梅图拉附近的一次无人机袭击中丧生</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-hezbollah-drone-strike/0000018f-5169-d6c3-afdf-5d7b6efc0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡被哈马斯的“是”所困，正在挑拨以色列和美国之间的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trapped-by-hamas-yes-is-driving-a-wedge-between-israel-and-the-u-s/0000018f-4f8f-d17f-adcf-ffef77d50000</link><description>鉴于过去几天的谈判危机，哈马斯宣布接受拟议的停火协议，这让以色列感到意外。 ■ 虽然耶路撒冷不断向埃及派遣代表团，但以色列国防军正在加大军事压力，并在埃及以东开展行动。拉法</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trapped-by-hamas-yes-is-driving-a-wedge-between-israel-and-the-u-s/0000018f-4f8f-d17f-adcf-ffef77d50000</guid></item></channel></rss>